<sections> 
  <clause id="_management_oversight_of_information_security" inline-header="false" obligation="normative"><title>Management oversight of information security</title><clause id="_general" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">   
  <title>General</title>   
  <requirement id="_d4eebd0c-f602-4d1f-bf85-2a05737cc88d"><label>/ss/584/2015/general/632</label><subject>The Cloud Service Provider’s management and board of directors</subject><description><p id="_bad01981-3d6e-421e-af66-c24adc2253d6">The Cloud Service Provider’s management and board of directors shall be responsible for the following requirements and audit procedures.</p>    
</description><specification exclude="true">     
  <p id="_7214995d-9855-4d3d-950e-eabac5f78943">be responsible for the following requirements and audit procedures</p>     
</specification></requirement>   
</clause>  
<clause id="_level_1_requirements_and_audit_procedures" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">   
  <title>Level 1 requirements and audit procedures</title>   
  <requirement id="_86804753-a3a4-4409-a7f5-b7f9e3de4adf"><label>/ss/584/2015/level/1</label><subject>The Cloud Service Provider’s management and board of directors</subject><specification exclude="false">     
  <ol id="_a64c9140-1571-4f5c-9d74-cc34a612a079" type="arabic">      
  <li>      
    <p id="_dafde1de-2d28-433a-9922-7fcabc7d4d1e">Managing information security risks related to people, process, technology and governance.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_672d9cb1-bc21-4582-88f0-83f88677d9df">Oversight of the effective implementation of the technology controls.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_3c69165c-754b-4cf9-a1ff-0a4278a187d3">Oversight of risk management practices.</p>      
  </li>      
</ol>     
</specification>
<verification exclude="false">     
  <ol id="_1230eca0-e6d7-442e-a383-c8eff21e391c" type="arabic">      
  <li>      
    <p id="_aa386f7d-53f3-4cf6-a041-ffcf18458bbb">Determine that the responsibilities of management and board of directors in managing and overseeing information security risks are documented and communicated.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_fa50f83a-585b-4cd7-997d-db213f97d7db">Inspect documents such as meeting minutes and committee charter to identify the participants involved in the meeting or committee, their respective job functions and the reporting relationship.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_76ca2f09-2eef-4304-a147-8621c57a73b5">Determine whether the management and board of directors meet regularly, at an appropriate and monitored frequency.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_3d7c8dba-0cb3-4017-bfe9-837030e396c0">Determine whether the information security function is headed by a Chief Information Security Officer (CISO) or similar function.</p>      
  </li>      
</ol>     
</verification></requirement>   
</clause>  
<clause id="_level_2_requirements_and_audit_procedures" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">   
  <title>Level 2 requirements and audit procedures</title>   
  <requirement id="_c421421d-58eb-4d0f-9d5d-ddce6ecdc7ff"><label>/ss/584/2015/level/2</label><inherit>/ss/584/2015/level/1</inherit><description><p id="_324465b7-be06-48f4-a978-a0858de101a1">The requirements and audit procedures are the same as those in Level 1.</p>    
</description><verification exclude="false"/></requirement>   
</clause>  
<clause id="_level_3_requirements_and_audit_procedures" inline-header="false" obligation="normative"><title>Level 3 requirements and audit procedures</title><requirement id="_0708c90a-a82e-4307-9971-d4568014df70"><label>/ss/584/2015/level/3</label><inherit>/ss/584/2015/level/2</inherit><description><p id="_4335501c-33fd-4b05-a41f-c95c3c191e29">The requirements are the same as those in Level 2.</p>    
</description><verification exclude="false"><p id="_b20c439c-a200-4ac2-a0a9-ea7385ec7b90">The audit procedures are those in Level 1 and the following:</p>     
<ol id="_23e6b73f-ed8e-4d63-9da1-210fdec809cd" type="arabic">      
  <li>      
    <p id="_7cdc49b7-3a15-4765-ae2b-f0384573e3bc">Verify risks have been reviewed, understood, and addressed (i.e. including a cost benefit analysis) by management and the board.</p>      
  </li>      
</ol></verification></requirement>   
